---
title: "US10 — Access the app after login"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SplashScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>AuthGateway → Supabase Auth
  A->>B: launch app
  B->>C: check session
  C->>G: currentSession
  G-->>C: session / null
  alt session valid
    C-->>B: signed in
    B-->>A: route to Home
  else no session
    C-->>B: signed out
    B-->>A: route to Login
  end
